 - Denim - gambar 1',1,1,'id-11134207-81ztg-me6p6h1uusxz9b','2026-06-27 07:04:27','2026-06-28 02:04:13'),(580,632,'produk/alur-cerita-x-nrp-aaima-abaya-katun-netral/variant-black-01.jpg','Alur Cerita X NRP Aaima Abaya Katun Netral - Black - gambar 1',1,1,'id-11134207-81ztn-me6p6h1utedj5e','2026-06-27 07:04:27','2026-06-28 02:04:13');
